tossup_question: -   –  Molly picks 4 coins out of her purse. Which of the following cannot be the total value, in cents, of the four coins?
bonus_question: -   –  A band produces an album with 14 songs. The band picks one of these songs to be released in April, a different one to be released in May, and a different one to be released in June. In how many different ways can this be done?
